title: Peter Kelly (Gaelic footballer)
text:
Peter Kelly is a <a href="Gaelic%20football">Gaelic football</a>er from <a href="County%20Kildare">County Kildare</a>. He plays for the <a href="Kildare%20GAA">Kildare</a> senior inter county football team and for his club <a href="Two%20Mile%20House%20GAA">Two Mile House</a>.
In October 2010, Kelly was named in the 2010 <a href="List%20of%20All%20Stars%20Awards%20winners%20%28football%29">All Stars Award</a> football team for his performances for Kildare during the <a href="2010%20All-Ireland%20Senior%20Football%20Championship">2010 season</a>; it was his first All Stars Award in his first season.
